Datatype extension for eZ Publish 4.x (License: GPL)
----------------------------------------------------

Datatype extension, 
that provides various iso codes datatype for ezpublish : IBAN, SWIFT/BIC, BBAN (RIB), Credit Card number, Bank Account number, etc.

Each code has its own validator. Each validator will be illustrated by a unit test.
Each time it is possible, these datatypes are built collectable & indexable.

